snippet.title: October 2023 Board of Regents Meeting
snippet.description:
The Board of Regents held its Board meeting on October 18, 2023, at the University of Louisiana at Lafayette. 

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Louisiana Board of Regents was created by the 1974 State Constitution and serves as the coordinating body for all public higher education in Louisiana.

LEARN MORE ABOUT REGENTS: https://www.laregents.edu
